{"tid":2339975,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"遭警棍打頭入ICU 助理無罪釋放","createTime":"2020-12-25T05:44:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T08:05:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4f895688111e9d6bf5d2250a05b5c223326e59c2","tid":2339975,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T05:44:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201225/FXZIBPBII5G3RP7I75GK64VOUM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201225%2FFXZIBPBII5G3RP7I75GK64VOUM%2F&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt4V%2FGdaNkEJkjxlYCjQUfm8%3D&h=1dbfe966\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201225%2FFXZIBPBII5G3RP7I75GK64VOUM%2F&h=c87d7e90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201225/FXZIBPBII5G3RP7I75GK64VOUM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n遭警棍打頭入ICU 助理無罪釋放<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_bNkH3kUUhvpRLVgrL5QWLYW4dU=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CS53EPLPQJBRTBWJVQYSE5SQPU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_bNkH3kUUhvpRLVgrL5QWLYW4dU%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCS53EPLPQJBRTBWJVQYSE5SQPU.jpg&h=45308558&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■被告陳樂文昨被裁定罪名不成立後離開法院。<br />\n<br />\n【藏雷射筆案】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年10月蒙面法生效，多區有市民遊行反對立法。一名實驗室助理在屯門街頭遭警方截停拘捕，被指藏有雷射筆，復遭警員用警棍打頭，事後需送院接受開顱手術，並一度入住深切治療部留醫。涉案助理及後被控在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪，案件昨裁決。裁判官李志豪指不應單憑被告的示威者裝束及現場環境，便指被告管有雷射筆的唯一合理推論是用作傷人，裁定被告罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n李官接納有關證物鏈證人及雷射筆專家證人供詞，裁定有關雷射筆的確從被告身上搜出，雷射筆未曾被干擾過，亦可傷人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官：憑裝束推論意圖不妥<br />\n<br />\n不過，李官指雷射筆並非攻擊性武器，雖然當時現場附近確有堵路出現，被告亦戴上示威物品，但若單憑被告裝束及現場環境，便推論被告藏有雷射筆的唯一意圖是傷人，既不穩妥亦不恰當。李官認為傷人只是其中一個推論，並非唯一推論，裁定被告罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n當日向被告扑頭的警員X早前獲准匿名出庭。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n辯方盤問時指，被告當時已將雙手放在胸前並張開雙掌，以示不反抗，但仍遭警員用警棍打頭打手。他曾要求X不要再打，惟X未理會，事後需送院接受開顱手術，放清瘀血，並入住深切治療部留醫，手部亦骨折。另有警員承認未有即場撿取被告身上的雷射筆，因他不認為屬危險品，亦不認為被告可用以傷害他及同袍。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：TMCC453/20"},{"pid":"465f31dcaee61aed831758425894e15f4e667932","tid":2339975,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T05:45:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8619ef54a76aa210da48732fc6bc2be092458f62","tid":2339975,"uid":148332,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T05:47:47.000Z","msg":"差d就死人，黑狗真係冇人性"},{"pid":"8a5528f970e3e71851a42060302de7b657fbc589","tid":2339975,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8619ef54a76aa210da48732fc6bc2be092458f62","tid":2339975,"uid":148332,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T05:47:47.000Z","msg":"差d就死人，黑狗真係冇人性"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T05:48:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd4ded98d107e6942f0b7e426e049bff3604329d","tid":2339975,"uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T05:48:56.000Z","msg":"另有警員承認未有即場撿取被告身上的雷射筆，因他不認為屬危險品，亦不認為被告可用以傷害他及同袍。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f39c434012d97227de63ff12e8d4e37c264f4e8","tid":2339975,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyT